THANK YOU, THANK YOU, THANK YOU to each of you for all the love and well wishes regarding my reelection to the #DeSotoTX City Council and for my selection as Mayor Pro Tem tonight! I was so honored to have my mom stand by my side this time. I'm returning texts and replying to comments as fast as I can 😆 Thank you @judgeambergivensdavis for administering my oath. 
Oh and thank you @sweetandchicboutique for the beautiful ensemble and thank you @sharlenabell for straightening out this mane of mine! 😘😘😘 [[[TAP FOR HAIR AND OUTFIT DETAILS]]. Thank you friends and family that came out tonight and to those that couldn't but still show your love! I see the kind gestures and they don't go unnoticed! Love each and every one of y'all and it's MY PLEASURE to serve this city. Thank you DeSoto for trusting me to do it all over again! #servantleader #electedofficial #yeo
